reviewText: Classic. ..This is my 5th time buying it over the years.
Tony Roberts is absolutely crazy, but in the best and funniest way. One of the funniest comedy videos that I've seen.

A friend had told me about this movie filmed in Newark NJ.
They talked about it so much that I had to check it out. This sketch video is classic and definatley goes down as a fav.
If you like Dave Chapelle or other skit based comedy you'll love this DVD.  Its hilarious.

buy this dvd used, watch it once.

it will take you back to church!

This one is for you. The ultimate in Black exploitation I've seen in a while. This is tasteless comedy. Some of the stuff is so ridiculous you have to laugh. But when you think about it you have to say why did they waste their time with the skits? They should just stuck to stand-up comedy.
